go-openexr
Copyright 2024-2025 Joshua Kaplan and the go-openexr contributors

This product is a pure Go implementation of the OpenEXR file format.
It does not contain any code from the reference C++ OpenEXR implementation,
but was developed with reference to the OpenEXR specification and file format
documentation.

